high_descs: Go to the door then turn left and head to the table
Pick up the potato from the right of the coffee maker
Turn around and go towards the sink then turn right and go to the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge, wait a bit, then take the potato out of the fridge
Turn right and go back to the table
Put the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato on the table

high_descs: Walk forward to the door and turn left towards the dining table.
Pick up the potato which is near the coffee machine on the table.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Cool the potato in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk to the dining table.
Put the potato on the dining table, to the left of the other potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled potato on a dining table.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, then turn left and walk up to the wooden table.
Pick up the rightmost potato off of the wooden table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the potato inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the potato, then close the fridge door.
Turn right and walk over to the wooden table.
Put the chilled potato on the counter to the left of the potato that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the wooden table.
